# terraform-first
### Parameters:

	You may need to change variables in variables.tf
	
##### * credentials.default 
    -> to your own local aws credential path
##### * pemfile.default 
    -> to your own local key path. project will automate save ssh rsa private key.

### Execute with command: 
	terraform init
	terraform plan
	terraform apply
	// terraform destroy
